Discovered a whole new side of Ibiza from our stay at @7PinesIbiza. From the magic of Es Vedrà & unimaginable sunsets in the west, to the iconic old town in the south & the awe-striking and serene coast in the north, the destination has something for everyone.

📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

Check out this stunning pool view by @pierreschuester! 🌊 We're sure you want to be here at Villas Flamingos too!🦩

Located in Mexico, this property champions conservation for both land and marine life, as well as giving guests unforgettable experiences to make them feel at home. There's plenty of opportunities to encounter wildlife from a distance, immerse in local culture, and reconnect with one's self by deeply immersing in the tropics. ❤

📽 @pierreschuester

Catching rainbows with @reneeroaming. 🌈 At Intercontinental French Polynesia, holidays can't be ruined by a little drizzle. 🌦️

Want to maximize this dream getaway? Step off the deck of your overwater villa into the warm embrace of their tranquil lagoon. Enjoy everything from scuba diving to sunset cruises to explore their majestic reefs and discover the thriving underwater wildlife. It's a once-in-a-lifetime experience so you better book that next flight to Bora Bora!

Tell us about your favorite tropical getaway stay. 💭 

📽️ @reneeroaming
📍 @icfr_polynesia
🎶 Israel Kamakawiwo'ole - Somewhere Over The Rainbow/What A Wonderful World

Basking in the glory of the rain with @antonio.pozo at Dusit Thani Maldives. 🌧️ Mood can't be dampened by any weather when you're staying at an overwater villa, don't you think?

At Dusit Thani Maldives, you'll have something to do rain or shine! Let the sounds of the rain melt away your stress while doing a yoga session with their resident yogi, or go on an excursion to swim with sharks and manta rays in the sea. 🌊

How was your last visit to the Maldives? Are you looking at flying there again? 🇲🇻

node.text:
Staycation views by @thetravelnova and @samishome. 😍 The Peninsula Hong Kong is not just for business, but it's also where you can let your hair down for a weekend staycation. Pampering, good food, and breathtaking views? One weekend, please! 🤩

Located in Tsim Sha Shui, the hotel opened in 1928 and has been a frontrunner in luxurious hospitality in Hong Kong ever since. The hotel's architecture and design combine colonial and modern elements, and is notable for its large fleet of Rolls-Royces painted a distinctive "Peninsula green". 

Have you stayed at the Peninsula? What are your recommendations when traveling to Hong Kong? 🇭🇰

📸 @thetravelnova, @samishome, @peninsulahongkong
📍@peninsulahongkong, Hong Kong

Leave all your worries and surrender yourself to luxurious Cypriot hospitality at Anassa. 🌴 This hillside retreat has an isolated beach with views of the Mediterranean Sea. 🌊

Have you had a thalassotherapy spa session? The resort is sure to pamper you so try this out!

💡 BH Tip: Make sure to have all necessary travel documents and passes for you to be able to enter the country. They may have opened their borders to tourists, but they encourage everyone to travel safely and to observe health protocols.

Is Cyprus on your travel list? What's the first thing you'll do once you visit? 🇨🇾

📍@anassa_resort, Paphos, Cyprus

Settling into golden hour with @momentsofgregory at the Amari Havodda Maldives. 🇲🇻 Isn’t this perfect for those working remotely? Cap off your day with stunning sunset views and a cocktail (or two). 😉

Do you miss those peaceful moments by the beach? Are you a fan of sunset views? 🌅 

📽️ @momentsofgregory

Perched atop a verdant peninsula cliff overlooking azure sea views, Makalele Domes Villas is a quirky, yet chic property that will leave you fascinated throughout your stay! ✨

It is one of the most recognized hotels in Lombok for its amazing aesthetic. Apart from gorgeous interiors and exemplary hospitality, the outdoor patios serve as a lounge area as you sit back and relax while sipping coconut juice or a cocktail! 🍹

💡BH Tip: The hotel's unique architecture is inspired by Wolfgang Widmoser, artist Salvador Dali's prodigy. 

Planning a trip to Indonesia? Would you stay here? 🇮🇩

📍@makaleledomes, Mentigi Bay, Lombok, Indonesia

Dreamy seaside views from morning to dusk at the Nautical Hotel. 🌅 Nestled in a secluded forest with a private beach, your vacation will be filled with warm Turkish hospitality and memorable moments by the sea! 🌊

💡 BH Tip: The hotel is the place to be for honeymooners looking for quality time. Thinking of surprising your significant other? Plan with the staff for a memorable seaside sunset dinner. Who knows, you might eventually be celebrating your anniversary with them a year after! 💍

Is Turkey included in your bucketlist? 🇹🇷 Share with us your most favorite memories here!

📍@nauticalhotel, Faralya Village, Turkey
